Use the standard library
This is how to sort_array of arr:
   Remember that n is arr's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that j is sum of i and 1
      When j is less than n, then:
         When item i in arr is more than item j in arr, then:
            Remember that tmp is item i in arr
            Remember that item i in arr is item j in arr
            Remember that item j in arr is tmp
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is arr
Now you know